        "Id": "d097df45-ec78-46bc-83bc-fe50e5d0fd4b",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Operation: Black Tide",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ROCKY_DUGONG",
        "PublicId": "134585445600",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Rocky/scene_dugong.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 87be73e8-64a2-4381-8438-013bb5d4f241).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rA rogue network has established a covert base on Ambrose Island. Under the cover of black-market trade, they are developing and distributing hazardous materials capable of destabilizing entire regions. This operation must be stopped.\r\rYour targets are four key individuals sustaining the network.\r\rThe commander, who transformed the island into a fortified hub.\rA technical specialist responsible for maintaining their volatile assets.\rA broker overseeing external transactions and securing resources.\rAnd a militia leader enforcing control through force and fear.\r\rEliminate them, and the network will collapse.\r\rAvoid collateral damage. Accidents are preferred.\r\rUse the island’s chaos and shadows to your advantage.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
        "GameVersion": "8.23.0.88",
